a4scan                                macro                               a4scan

NAME
     aa44ssccaann - four-motor scan

SYNOPSIS

     aa44ssccaann mm11 ssttaarrtt11 eenndd11 mm22 ssttaarrtt22 eenndd22 mm33 ssttaarrtt33 eenndd33 ssttaarrtt44 eenndd44 iinntteerrvvaallss
     ttiimmee

DESCRIPTION

     aa44ssccaann scans four motors, as specified by mm11, mm22, mm33 and mm44.  Each motor
     moves the same number of intervals with starting and ending positions given
     by ssttaarrtt11 and eenndd11, ssttaarrtt22 and eenndd22, ssttaarrtt33 and eenndd33, ssttaarrtt44 and eenndd44,
     respectively.  The step size for each motor is ((ssttaarrtt--eenndd))//iinntteerrvvaallss.  The
     number of data points collected will be iinntteerrvvaallss++11.  Count time is given
     by ttiimmee, which if positive, specifies seconds and if negative, specifies
     monitor counts.

EXAMPLE

     aa44ssccaann eell11 00 1100 eell22 00 1100 eell33 00 1100 eell44 00 1100 2200 1100

